-[Deena] I don't know.

27:37.250 --> 27:38.166
I guess…

27:38.250 --> 27:40.041
Sometimes accidents just happen.

27:40.125 --> 27:41.666
We lost control, sir.

27:41.750 --> 27:43.083
Freak accident.

27:43.750 --> 27:45.875
Suck it, pig.

27:46.458 --> 27:47.916
It was just an accident.

27:50.041 --> 27:51.125
Alright.

27:51.208 --> 27:54.000
Well, if you do think of anything,

27:54.583 --> 27:55.625
give me a call.

27:57.500 --> 27:58.625
I'm on your side.

27:59.125 --> 28:00.666
Yeah, totally.

28:05.875 --> 28:08.000
My car is totaled.

28:08.083 --> 28:10.041
Well, Daddy will buy you a new one.

28:15.083 --> 28:17.166
-[Deena grunts]
-[Peter] Shittyside trash.

28:17.250 --> 28:20.166
You are all fucking… dead.

28:29.166 --> 28:34.833
[indistinct voices whispering]

28:36.583 --> 28:41.416
[menacing music crescendos]

28:41.500 --> 28:42.625
[screaming]

28:46.250 --> 28:48.875
[dog barking]

28:50.416 --> 28:53.375
[children laughing, playing]

28:59.500 --> 29:04.041
[soft suspenseful music playing]

29:13.916 --> 29:16.125
[gasping]

29:16.791 --> 29:18.458
-I'm gonna kill you.
-[Josh] Yeah?

29:18.541 --> 29:21.000
Do it before Dad gets here,
he's gonna murder you!

29:21.583 --> 29:25.041
You know the cops called him at work
about some accident last night?

29:25.125 --> 29:26.250
Please get out of my room.

29:26.333 --> 29:28.625
You get out of your room.
You've been in your bed all day!

29:30.625 --> 29:31.833
Get up!

29:34.291 --> 29:36.125
[ominous bell rings]

29:41.333 --> 29:43.458
[female reporter] I'm here
with Martin P. Franklin,

29:43.541 --> 29:44.958
Shadyside Mall Janitor.

29:45.041 --> 29:47.916
-Martin, what do you know?
-[Martin] He was a normal dude.

29:48.000 --> 29:52.666
Always thought he would, like, just go
home and read a comic book or whatever.

29:52.750 --> 29:55.250
He was chill, just snapped I guess.

29:55.833 --> 29:57.750
[female reporter] A baffling development

29:57.833 --> 30:02.041
as mall employee Ryan Torres
has been identified as the killer.

30:02.125 --> 30:04.333
A recent graduate of Shadyside High

30:04.416 --> 30:07.333
an ordinary guy who,
as those who knew him attest,

30:07.416 --> 30:09.000
just seemed to snap.

30:09.083 --> 30:11.791
-[ringing tone]
-[woman] East Union Medical.

30:11.875 --> 30:14.708
Hi. Uh, Samantha Fraser's room, please?

30:14.791 --> 30:17.125
-[rock music playing upstairs]
-[doorbell rings]

30:17.208 --> 30:18.833
Josh! Get the door!

30:18.916 --> 30:20.375
["More Human Than Human" playing]

30:20.458 --> 30:23.125
♪ Man, I turn the world around
With a skeleton hand ♪

30:23.208 --> 30:25.916
♪ Say I am electric head ♪

30:26.000 --> 30:27.125
[doorbell rings]

30:27.208 --> 30:30.916
-[woman] Hello?
-[Deena] Uh… Hi, uh, Mrs. Fraser.

30:31.000 --> 30:33.500
I'm sorry. Uh, Miss… Ms…

30:33.583 --> 30:35.583
-[doorbell rings]
-Hi, um…

30:35.666 --> 30:37.333
-[doorbell]
-Is Sam there? I just…

30:38.000 --> 30:40.750
-I wanted to see how she was doing.
-[Ms. Fraser] Deena?

30:41.375 --> 30:43.208
Yeah. Hi.

30:44.416 --> 30:46.500
I was just w… worried about her and--

30:46.583 --> 30:50.375
[Ms. Fraser] You won't stop until you've
ruined her life completely, will you?

30:50.458 --> 30:53.458
-She's fine. Don't call here again.
-[line goes dead]

30:54.375 --> 30:56.416
[dead tone]

30:56.500 --> 30:59.416
-[doorbell rings repeatedly]
-Josh!

30:59.500 --> 31:03.125
♪ More human than human
More human than hu-- ♪

31:12.333 --> 31:13.333
Hello?

31:14.458 --> 31:18.041
[menacing music playing]

31:19.250 --> 31:20.500
[door creaking]

31:25.666 --> 31:27.000
[ominous drumbeat]

31:29.666 --> 31:31.375
Oh, hey, Peter!

31:31.458 --> 31:33.416
See you got the full costume now!

31:38.291 --> 31:40.458
[door creaking]

31:41.875 --> 31:44.083
[menacing music crescendos]

31:44.166 --> 31:45.708
-[timer buzzing]
-[Josh] Hey!

31:45.791 --> 31:46.708
[gasps]

31:46.791 --> 31:49.041
-Pizza ready?
-Oh, that ringing you heard.

31:49.791 --> 31:50.875
What? [scoffs]

31:51.500 --> 31:52.958
I have priorities.

31:53.041 --> 31:54.291
Jeez.

31:55.541 --> 31:58.291
-[buzzer stops]
-Shit! Hot, hot, hot!

32:02.583 --> 32:08.333
[ominous music playing]

32:09.166 --> 32:10.750
Sunnyvale prick.

32:14.791 --> 32:16.458
Holy shit!

32:16.541 --> 32:17.583
[Deena] Stay here.

32:22.250 --> 32:23.500
You're pathetic!

32:26.750 --> 32:28.375
[ominous music playing]

32:28.458 --> 32:29.958
["Gz and Hustlas" playing]

32:30.041 --> 32:31.333
[Kate] Four in each bag.

32:31.416 --> 32:32.666
If you finish in an hour,

32:32.750 --> 32:34.958
