My So-Called Life with me.

32:39.375 --> 32:41.000
And, uh, do not eat these.

32:41.083 --> 32:44.125
These will make your little hearts stop,
you'll choke to death on vomit

32:44.208 --> 32:46.500
and everyone will be so, so super sad.

32:47.375 --> 32:48.208
