and this was all I had in the car.

33:16.541 --> 33:18.666
So, yes. Yes, I am.

33:18.750 --> 33:20.541
-[pager beeping]
-Oh.

33:22.083 --> 33:24.208
That's disgusting. You're disgusting.

33:27.916 --> 33:30.541
-[man 1 on TV] Alright, kiddo?
-[man 2] There I was at ten…

33:30.625 --> 33:32.166
