in one of those skull masks. It's fucked.

33:50.208 --> 33:51.958
[sighs] I gotta go. Call you back.

34:00.000 --> 34:01.666
Jesus! Put something on!

34:01.750 --> 34:03.916
What? Make up your mind, woman!

34:04.000 --> 34:05.458
[window smashes]

34:07.916 --> 34:08.833
Stay here.

34:09.750 --> 34:11.750
[low ominous music playing]

34:14.958 --> 34:17.000
[glass smashing]

34:21.958 --> 34:24.833
[glass smashing, banging]

34:25.666 --> 34:27.458
[banging]

34:29.750 --> 34:32.125
-[whispering] Maybe this isn't a good id--
-Shh!

34:40.208 --> 34:41.916
Hey, creeper. What the f--

34:42.000 --> 34:44.750
[haunting music playing]

34:44.833 --> 34:48.416
-[quietly] Are you crazy?
-[Kate] It's just that Sunnyvale asshole.

34:52.125 --> 34:53.541
[door creaks]

35:12.250 --> 35:13.333
Thank you so much.

35:13.416 --> 35:16.000
Oh, no. I'm so happy to have the company.

35:17.916 --> 35:21.166
