38:30.958 --> 38:32.833
Yo, Si-Money. Cash me.

38:33.458 --> 38:35.833
Don't look at me, dude.
I'm… I'm… I'm broke.

38:36.416 --> 38:37.375
You got any change?

38:41.375 --> 38:42.416
Oh, um…

38:44.958 --> 38:45.958
